{"tid":534490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後萬寧賣印花就得","createTime":"2018-01-20T00:22:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T08:49:13.000Z","uid":53553,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5a071bccebde9cfb633aac81ba1d8ce3f199141f","tid":534490,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T00:22:12.000Z","msg":"萬寧最貴既係印花<br />\n最多人想要又係印花<br />\n以後淨係賣印花都賺撚到你傻<br />\n而家真係萬寧轉行既最好時機<br />\n<br />\n計返條數<br />\n又賣奶粉又賣藥你賺得幾多都係比個租<br />\n你排到成間鋪都係貨，一個月大大話話都要交返十幾萬租<br />\n而家香港有成350間萬寧，乘返開一年要比成三五億租<br />\n仲未計人工同燈油火蠟<br />\n萬寧係咪當自己開善堂做蝕本生意益街坊?<br />\n<br />\n不如趁今次一鋪返身，全線改賣印花算<br />\n你一個印花賣50蚊，當你一間鋪一日賣3000個印花(保守估計)<br />\n300幾間鋪一日就已經賺左500萬<br />\n一個月已經一億五千萬<br />\n而呢300間鋪係唔使租得貴，賣印花需要一個counter位就夠<br />\n你是但請個最低工資既阿嬸都可以做呢個位<br />\n計返一個月每間鋪都係使你2皮，乘返開1000萬都唔使<br />\n咁你一個月純利都已經成一億四千萬(當你扣埋印花既成本)<br />\n一年已經可以淨袋15億<br />\n<br />\n之後再北上發展<br />\n700萬人都已經比你賺到15億<br />\n而家中國發展得咁好，生活水平已經同香港一樣<br />\n14億除返700萬再乘15億<br />\n屌你老味一年已經3000億純利仲癲撚過騰訊<br />\n咪話唔教精你，之後再整埋印花支付﹑印花寶<br />\n整D電子印花出來，連生產成本都慳返<br />\n再開發埋用印花買基金同保險<br />\n然後再下一城整埋VR印花同AI印花<br />\n到時真係連馬雲都要同你含撚"},{"pid":"6134899cc87d7d4ac1b7ac67b55788480b7750ef","tid":534490,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T00:51:16.000Z","msg":"8.5/10"},{"pid":"6eda385d7a53baed2ec67a350695e5dc5715afca","tid":534490,"uid":12449,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T00:51:46.000Z","msg":"出印花幣就得啦 之後慢慢炒起佢"},{"pid":"6eca684061ca2a685146fa5f2c2b479dd8093cf9","tid":534490,"uid":77191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T00:55:45.000Z","msg":"痴線 但我鍾意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52595a17d4cacb37f2c5b5554b89fdadf7f9d827","tid":534490,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T00:57:40.000Z","msg":"萬寧高層食撚屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 整十隻萬寧貓都翻唔到身呀"},{"pid":"9256c6fd75eeca7c61730dee8340f70c8935bdfd","tid":534490,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c971b51f1bba4c3d9ac630f2bd1b05b92ee9bf3d","tid":534490,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9256c6fd75eeca7c61730dee8340f70c8935bdfd","tid":534490,"uid":53553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T01:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb3a6ca8b20b6397ea89538f221f6de48fc4c2b","tid":534490,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b703ea1b1f8e9707d6ce083dfa4b5e578e9ef782","tid":534490,"uid":148724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T08:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}